    "\n",
    "# Exercise E3 – Cartopy Mapping  \n",
    "**Name:** Asanda Mthembu  \n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook produces:\n",
    "1. A map of Antarctica and the Southern Ocean (south of 60°S)  \n",
    "2. A map of the South Atlantic (20°S–50°S) with selected coastal cities  \n",
    "\n",
    "The maps were created using Cartopy, with careful selection of projection, extent, and visual styling to improve readability and spatial accuracy.\n",
    "\n",
    "Write a notebook to produce the following maps\n",
    "\n",
    "The Antarctic continent and the Southern Ocean starting from 60°S\n",
    "The South Atlantic, from 20°S to 50°S. The map should show the following locations: Walvis Bay, Cape Town, Rio de Janeiro, Montevideo"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "e843cb96-e8f8-4fd0-8179-16a9c23d4ebb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import cartopy.crs as ccrs\n",
    "import cartopy\n",
    "import cartopy.feature as cfeature\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "# these modules will be used later\n",
    "from geopy.geocoders import Nominatim\n",
    "from geopy.distance import geodesic"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d729a5dd-9cbf-4acc-8db4-6f23badd1633",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Exercise 1 : South Pole"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 13,
   "id": "38b4dd59-d8ab-44dc-aef2-190bdca09bf5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 800x800 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))\n",
    "\n",
    "ax = plt.axes(projection=ccrs.SouthPolarStereo())\n",
    "\n",
    "# Southern Ocean extent\n",
    "ax.set_extent([-180, 180, -90, -60], crs=ccrs.PlateCarree())\n",
    "\n",
    "# Features \n",
    "ax.add_feature(cfeature.OCEAN)\n",
    "ax.add_feature(cfeature.LAND, facecolor='lightgrey')\n",
    "ax.add_feature(cfeature.COASTLINE, linewidth=0.8)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Gridlines \n",
    "gl = ax.gridlines(draw_labels=True, linestyle='--', alpha=0.4)\n",
    "gl.top_labels = False\n",
    "gl.right_labels = False\n",
    "gl.xlabel_style = {'size': 9}\n",
    "gl.ylabel_style = {'size': 9}\n",
    "\n",
    "#  Title \n",
    "plt.title('Antarctica and the Southern Ocean (South of 60°S)', fontsize=13, pad=10)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
